dataprimeQuery.text:
source logs
| filter $d.severity:string == $p.Severity:string
| choose $m.timestamp.formatTimestamp() as Time, $d.message as message

source logs
| filter $d.tags != null
#| filter arrayContains($d.tags,'beats_input_codec_plain_applied')
| choose $d.tags, $m.severity, $m.priorityclass
| groupby ($m.timestamp / 10m).formatTimestamp() as timestamp agg count_if($m.priorityclass==$p.priority:string  && ( $m.severity == INFO || arrayContains($d.tags, $p.tag:string))) as count

source logs
| filter $p.applicationName.arrayContains($l.applicationname)
| groupby $m.timestamp / $p.timeRange.suggestedInterval as timestamp, $l.applicationname as application agg count() as count

source logs
| groupby $l.subsystemname agg count() as count

source logs
| filter $m.timestamp != null
| groupby roundTime($m.timestamp,10m).formatTimestamp('%FT%H:%M',tz='utc') as timestamp agg count() as count
source logs | groupby $m.timestamp / $p.timeRange.suggestedInterval as timestamp agg count() as count
